{{main|{{le|福斗鈾濃縮工廠|Fordow Fuel Enrichment Plant}}}}

福斗鈾濃縮工廠位於庫姆東北20英里處。<ref>[http://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/russia-regrets-reported-iran-nuclear-activity-in-qom-facility-1.406555 Russia 'regrets' reported Iran nuclear activity in Qom facility] {{Wayback|url=http://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/russia-regrets-reported-iran-nuclear-activity-in-qom-facility-1.406555 |date=20150726202604 }}, [[Haaretz|Haaretz]], January 10, 2012.</ref>[[國際原子能機構|國際原子能機構]]（IAEA）在2012年1月宣布，伊朗已開始生產用於醫療的濃縮鈾，鈾的濃度最高可達20％，而且這種產品“受到IAEA的控制和監視。”<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-16470100 |title=Iran enriching uranium at Fordo plant near Qom |publisher=BBC |date=10 January 2012 |access-date=1 March 2012 |archive-date=2021-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210517074033/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-16470100 |dead-url=no }}</ref>伊朗當局表示，濃縮工廠建於山中深處，以預防[[以色列|以色列]]不斷提出要攻擊這座工廠的威脅，以色列認為這座工廠所產的濃縮鈾可用作核子武器用途。<ref>{{cite web|author=Azmat Khan|url=https://www.pbs.org/wgbh/pages/frontline/government-elections-politics/did-santorum-suggest-iran-wants-nukes-to-bring-back-messiah|title=Did Santorum Suggest Iran Wants Nukes to Bring Back Messiah?|publisher=[[Public_Broadcasting_Service|Public Broadcasting Service]]|date=13 January 2012|access-date=2021-04-27|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924161042/http://www.pbs.org/wgbh/pages/frontline/government-elections-politics/did-santorum-suggest-iran-wants-nukes-to-bring-back-messiah/|dead-url=no}}</ref>然而，攻擊如此接近什葉派伊斯蘭教聖城的核子設施，有引起什葉派教派報復的風險。<ref>{{cite web|author=Akluf Benn|url=http://www.haaretz.com/print-edition/opinion/cries-of-hold-me-back-may-lead-israel-to-strike-iran-1.6986|title=Cries of 'hold me back' may lead Israel to strike Iran|publisher=Haaretz.com|date=3 September 2009|access-date=2021-04-27|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924231804/http://www.haaretz.com/print-edition/opinion/cries-of-hold-me-back-may-lead-israel-to-strike-iran-1.6986|dead-url=no}}</ref>

